A mule, which many people don't know is one of the hottest shoe trends right now.&nbsp; Fashion and trends are always evolving, and the mule has made a blast from the past. As the original mule was created in the 16th century, they came back on the scene when Actress and model Icon Marilyn Monroe started wearing them in the 1950's. They became popular again in the 1990's and have now hit the streets of fashion and are a must have for every fashion diva.&nbsp; A mule is a shoe that is backless and often closed-toed. Mule's can be high heels or flats and majority worn by women, But we've seen here in Mzansi our very own male celebs like Riky Rick and the Major League twins rocks the mules.&nbsp; This shoe is a great alternative to your regularly pump or sneaker. Change it up by choosing between flat or high heel mules.&nbsp; There are all kinds of mules that can fit your personality and comfort.&nbsp; Wear mules to look like a fashion diva without even trying. &nbsp;